      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this impeccably preserved specimen, currently offered in showroom-grade condition. This vehicle has been curated to the highest standards of automotive excellence, exhibiting no discernible wear and retaining its original factory luster throughout. Every mechanical and aesthetic detail has been rigorously vetted to ensure it meets the exacting requirements of the most discerning collector. This represents an unrivaled opportunity to acquire a vehicle of significant pedigree and flawless presentation.",
