    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presenting an exemplary specimen of automotive excellence, maintained to an uncompromising standard. This vehicle remains in pristine showroom condition, featuring an unblemished exterior finish and a cabin that retains its original factory luster. Every mechanical component has been rigorously vetted to ensure peak performance, offering a driving experience indistinguishable from a new acquisition. This is an investment-grade vehicle for the discerning collector who demands nothing less than perfection.",
      "price": 48500.0,
