    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! You seriously have to see this beauty in person to believe it. I have absolutely babied this car since the day I got it, and it's still in total showroom condition! It looks and drives just like it did when it first rolled off the lot\u2014not a single flaw to be found. I'm so excited for the next owner to enjoy it as much as I have. It\u2019s a total gem that\u2019s been kept in a climate-controlled garage and polished to perfection. Come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
